    General Stores in Powai, Mumbai

    General stores or mom-n-pop shops are known as 'kiranas' in most parts of the country. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. The vast list of general store items does not limit to food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. These store owners work in conjunction with wholesalers, distributors, and retailers forming a wide network in the city or town. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Powai, Mumbai from the list given above.
